file.name: propertiesWithConstraints.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
components:
  schemas:
    TestComponent:
      title: TestComponent
      description: 'Test component description'
      type: object
      properties:
        noConstraint:
          type: string
        minLengthConstraint:
          type: string
          minLength: 42
        maxLengthConstraint:
          type: string
          maxLength: 42
        bothLengthsConstraint:
          type: string
          minLength: 3
          maxLength: 42
        patternConstraint:
          type: string
          pattern: '^[A-Z]$'
        allConstraint:
          type: string
          minLength: 3
          maxLength: 42
          pattern: '^[A-Z]$'
